{"pageProps":{"data":"<h5>extends</h5>\n<p>继承：</p>\n<ul>\n    <li>子类会继承父类的属性和方法</li>\n    <li>构造函数不会被继承，通过 super 的形式向父类传入初始化值。</li>\n    <li>子类能复写父类的方法 getter 、setter</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>super</h5>\n<p>在继承后的子类中，需要给父类的构造函数传值，通过使用 super 指向父类，然后初始化父类中需要的值：</p>\n<code class=\"c\">\n    <span class=\"p\">class One{</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">String a;</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">int b;</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">One(this.a,this.b);</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">say(){</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">print(\"${this.a} -- ${this.b}\");</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">class Two Extends One{</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">Two(super.a,super.b);</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code>\n<p>也可以使用这种方法：</p>\n<code class=\"c\">\n    <span class=\"p\">class One{</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">String a;</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">int b;</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">One(this.a,this.b);</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">say(){</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">print(\"${this.a} -- ${this.b}\");</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">class Two Extends One{</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">Two(a,b):super(a,b){}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code>\n<p>也可以给命名构造方法传参：</p>\n<code class=\"c\">\n    <span class=\"p\">class One{</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">String a;</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">int b;</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">One(this.a,this.b);</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">One.n(this.a,this.b);</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">say(){</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">print(\"${this.a} -- ${this.b}\");</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">class Two Extends One{</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">Two(a,b):super.n(a,b){}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code>\n<h5>覆写</h5>\n<p>在子类中覆写父类的方法，正常加 @override：</p>\n<code class=\"c\">\n    <span class=\"p\">@override <span class=\"r\">// 覆写声明，可不写，但是建议写</span></span>\n    <span class=\"p\">p(){print(name);}</span>\n</code>\n<h5>mixins</h5>\n<p>Dart 中无法同时继承多各类（这点和 implement 不同)。可以使用 mixins 来实现这样的需求： </p>\n<code class=\"c\">\n    <span class=\"p\"></span>\n    <span class=\"p\">void main(){</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">var a = new Lm();</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">a.p(); <span class=\"r\">// 有顺序的覆盖</span></span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\"></span>\n    <span class=\"p\">class Lms{</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">p(){</span>\n    <span class=\"p4\">print(\"Lms\");</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\"></span>\n    <span class=\"p\">class Lmssee{</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">p(){</span>\n    <span class=\"p4\">print(\"Lmssee\");</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\"></span>\n    <span class=\"p\">class lm with Lms, Lmssee{ <span class=\"r\">// 先后顺序影响到方法或属性的值</span></span>\n    <span class=\"p2\"></span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code>\n<ul>\n    <li>mixins 只能是普通类</li>\n    <li>mixins 类不能有构造方法</li>\n</ul>\n<code class=\"c\">\n    <span class=\"p\"></span>\n    <span class=\"p\">void main(){</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">var a = new Lm();</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">a.p(); <span class=\"r\">// 有顺序的覆盖</span></span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\"></span>\n    <span class=\"p\">class Lms{</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">p(){</span>\n    <span class=\"p4\">print(\"Lms\");</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\"></span>\n    <span class=\"p\">class Lmssee{</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">p(){</span>\n    <span class=\"p4\">print(\"Lmssee\");</span>\n    <span class=\"p2\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"p\"></span>\n    <span class=\"p\">class lm with Lms, Lmssee{ <span class=\"r\">// 先后顺序影响到方法或属性的值</span></span>\n    <span class=\"p2\"></span>\n    <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code>","pageTitle":"flutter ✈︎✈︎ dart ✈︎✈︎ class","title":"继承"},"__N_SSG":true}